<br>
  As for Frogloks, I am happy to have them as allies, but I have yet to form a decision about this new race.  ( all in characters sentiments, of course. )<br>
<br>
At any rate, that brings me to another point to add about the guild.  I would love to have some others interested in playing a Tolkein inspired roll.  I know, this isn't Middle Earth, but RP is subjective, isn't it?<br>
